        expr rv(ctx,Z3_mk_int2real(ctx,iv));
        return rv;
    }

Then ,“a&5” may be wrote as followed:
```
context ctx;
expr a=ctx.real_const("a");
expr b=ctx.real_val("5");
expr av=Z3_real2bv(a,ctx);
expr bv=Z3_real2bv(b,ctx);
