During the change to the super duper amazing interactive CLI, however, we changed this.  IMHO, the new output is far less useful, particularly because in CI you'll often be trying to debug what happened after the fact.  We can also echo lines for the same resource multiple times, depending on the arrival of certain events, which leads to confusing output.

If we're going to keep the current output, I think we need to make it a little clearer that events are paired (begin/end) somehow.  Alternatively, we could go back to something like the old output which, given that this is our "build log format" in the service already, feels like the right call to me.

